Hello! Welcome to West Barnstable Horse Hides, your favorite neighborhood bowling alley. My name is Jake. How can I assist you today?

Hi Jake. I have some questions about a bill I received. My name is Lisa.

Nice to meet you, Lisa. I can definitely help with that. Can you please provide the invoice number on your bill?

Sure, the invoice number is two three four five.

Thank you for that, Lisa. Now, could you also verify your email address associated with the account?

Yes, it's lisa.smith@email.com.

Got it. Let me quickly check the details for you. Just a moment, please.

Thanks for waiting, Lisa. I've reviewed your account and there was a minor error in the last billing cycle. I have corrected it and you should see a refund of one five zero in your account within five to seven business days.

Oh, that’s great to hear! Thank you so much, Jake.

You're welcome, Lisa. If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Thank you for choosing West Barnstable Horse Hides, and have a fantastic day!
